channel.title: Make clients work! =O
channel.description:
Ok i just found this out and, to make ALL clients work, (must have a EGUI,java file) right click runserver, click edit, replace everything its got in it to [code]@echo off javac -cp .;sign *.java java -cp . EGUI pause[/code] Save and run!
Credits- 75% Mod taharok for his SSB 5.0 Ultimate thing 25% Me for finding out how to make clients work!
